snippet.title: Chibi-Robo!: Photo Finder - 55 Minute Playthrough [3DS]
snippet.description:
Playing through 55 minutes of Chibi-Robo!: Photo Finder for the Nintendo 3DS. Snapping a couple photos for the Nostaljunk musuem and performing jobs for Happy Points.

Game: Chibi-Robo!: Photo Finder
Platform: Nintendo 3DS (eShop)
Price: $9.99
